org.opendaylight.controller.sal.match

Enum MatchType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MatchType>
      • org.opendaylight.controller.sal.match.MatchType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MatchType>

    public enum MatchType
extends java.lang.Enum<MatchType>
    Represents the binding between the id, the value and mask type and the range values of the elements type that can be matched on the network frame/packet/message
